						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 16 <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> for burning a light during the evening service in the temple of Ūrbāgaṅkoṇḍaruḷiya-Nāyanār, by Maṅgalaṅkiḻāṉ Aimboḻil-Rāmaṉ of Māṇḍaiyūr in Tirumuṉaippāḍi-nāḍu. This was deposited with a <hi rend="italic">Śivabrāhmaṇa</hi> of the temple.</p>						

						</summary>
